		code border-{side}
		|  for 
		code xs
		|  and 
		code border-{breakpoint}-{side}
		|  for 
		code sm
		| , 
		code md
		| , 
		code lg
		| ,  
		code xl
		| , and 
		code xxl
		| .
	p.font-sans-serif
		| Where
		em  side
		|  is one of:
	ul
		li
			code top
			|  - for classes that set style for 
			code border-top
		li
			code bottom
			|  - for  classes that set style for 
			code border-bottom
		li
			code left
			|  - for  classes that set style for 
