mixin BorderColorWidth
	p Border color set as 
		code currentColor
		|  and border width 
		code 1px
		| . Modifier can be used to change border color and width. The modifier classes for color are named using the format 
		code border-{color}
		|  and for width 
		code border-2
		| .
	p
		| Where
		em  color
		|  is one of: 
		each val in colorsAll
			code #{val}
			| , 

	h5.mt-4 Examples
	+ComponentCard
		.component-example
			each val in colorsAll
				= '\n'
				span.border(class=`border-${val} text-${val}`)=val
				= '\n'
			span.border.border-2 2
		= '\n'	

